source.name: Park & Ride
source.description: The City and County of Honolulu, Department of Transportation Services, operates Hawaii Kai, Mililani, and Royal Kunia Park & Ride facilities. Park & Ride facilities are transit stations where bus patrons, and future rail patrons, may drive to the facility, leave their car during the day and catch TheBus.
